title: US strategy document says Europe risks 'civilisational erasure'
description: BERLIN, Dec 5 (Reuters) - Europe faces "civilisational erasure" and must change course if it is to remain a reliable ally for the United States, according to a U.S. National Security Strategy posted on the White House website. Read full story
